The '''Szczecin Art Academy''' ({{lang-pl|Akademia Sztuki w Szczecinie}}) is a [[public university]] in [[Szczecin]], [[Poland]], founded on September 1, 2010. The profile of the university includes both [[music]] and [[visual arts]] with programmes offered in two different art disciplines. It consists of 4 faculties with BA and MA courses.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.akademiasztuki.eu/en/academy/faculties |archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20141126193428/http%3A//www.akademiasztuki.eu/en/academy/faculties |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2014-11-26 |title=Akademia Sztuki &#124; faculties |publisher=Akademiasztuki.eu |date= |accessdate=2012-08-07 |quote=[http://www.akademiasztuki.eu/en/academy/about (About)] }}</ref>
