== Awards and nominations ==
{{BLP sources section|date=April 2015}}
Hunt has been recognized extensively in her career. In 1998 she won a [[Golden Globe Award]], an [[Academy Awards|Academy Award]] and an [[Emmy Award]]. Hunt was nominated for a [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Lead Actress in a Comedy Series]] seven years in a row, from 1993 through 1999, winning in the last four years.<ref name="emmys">[http://www.emmys.com/ Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]. Emmys.com.</ref>

